prevention of colds and flu 
the most common misconception is its not serious said dr 
walter gunn an epidemiologist at the centers for disease control 
in atlanta 
most who succumb are elderly or people with chronic health 
problems they should be vaccinated now to be ready for the flu 
season usually beginning in december in some years flu claims 
twice or more the annual rate of 20000 
because of people getting together for the thanskgiving 
holiday traveling from other places spending a few days together 
inside the house thats a perfect environment for spreading the 
virus around said mary huck spokeswoman for the illinois 
