similar as possible to the enthronements of the past two emperors 
it was during that period that the government reformed 
shintoism japans highly decentralized indigenous religion into a 
centralized state religion used to glorify the emperor and rally 
support for the government especially during world war ii 
the government is trying to create a unifying nationalistic 
force using the same process as in the past kawane says for 
example the parliament is debating a law that would allow the 
dispatch of japanese troops overseas what purpose would japanese 
soldiers be willing to die for now not very many people want to 
die for the prime minister 
