agriculture chief henry voss 
they officially lifted a quarantine barring movement of fruit 
and vegetables from infested areas medfly traps will continue to 
be placed statewide to detect any new arrivals 
the arrival of illegal fruit and vegetables usually carried in 
travelers luggage virtually ensures future infestations one 
