it takes is one person 
quarantines had been imposed because of worries that medflies 
could spread from urban southern california to rural agricultural 
areas and wreck the states 18 billionayear farming economy 
slightly smaller than a common housefly the medfly lays its 
eggs in fruit and vegetables the can afflict hundreds of different 
plant varieties 
