s gorbachev who arrived in bonn today to a 27man military honor 
guard 
the soviet presidents visit is highly symbolic since his 
reforms helped collapse the iron curtain and open the berlin wall 
he was to sign a 20year germansoviet nonaggression treaty and 
was expected to receive financial aid for his nations troubled 
economy 
