it doesnt look like it does it 
weve run into volvos that have stood out in a pile of cars as 
being tougher said blaeser 23 of chippewa falls wis 
volvo spokesman robert austin watched the car stomping on 
television from his office and said while the volvos didnt come 
out unscathed they appeared to hold up well compared with other 
cars 
at one point the predator got stuck on the volvo on its third 
pass over the five cars 
it was apparent that the volvo was standing up to the full 
weight of the truck so i would leave it to the public to draw 
their own conclusions austin said 
