cyanide or potassium cyanide inkulis said 
it was not clear how the leak occurred 
it was impossible to determine how many people were affected in 
latvia or byelorussia because many have begun using well water in 
recent years 
riga is the largest city on the river lying at its mouth on the 
baltic sea but hundreds possibly thousands of other people live 
in areas along the river and traditionally used the river for food 
and drinking water 
