a national organization that has 
represented young farmers for more than a half century is making 
changes to adapt to an era of farmers with business suits and mbas 
who work with computerized tractors 
but some fear the spirit of the traditional farmer may be lost 
in the shuffle 
two years ago to keep up with the times future farmers of 
