that cia stations and facilities in honduras and el salvador were 
all deeply involved in the resupply operation according to 
a recent federal appeals court decision and court papers filed in 
the case 
in court papers fernandez said he would have shown who at the 
cia supported the resupply operation how they did it where they 
did it why they did it and who else at the cia knew about it 
one period walshs investigators are focusing on is october 
1986 according to the sources on oct 5 of that year a resupply 
plane in norths network was shot down over nicaragua triggering a 
political firestorm on capitol hill and threatening to expose the 
operation 
reagan abrams and others in the administration stated 
