congress destroying documents and accepting an illegal gratuity in 
the scandal but a federal appeals court panel set aside the 
conviction poindexter was convicted in april of conspiracy two 
counts of obstruction and two counts of making false statements he 
is appealing six other people have entered guilty pleas or been 
convicted in jury trials in the affair 
