<TEXT>
if you look for a spark of life in the stock 
market these days the search pretty much begins and ends with 
electric utility issues 
while the dow jones average of 30 industrials was climbing to 
record highs near the 3000 mark earlier this year the electric 
utility group languished in disfavor 
but since late summer as fears of recession gripped the 
markets the roles have been reversed from its low point for the 
year on aug 24 through nov 2 dow joness average of 15 utilities 
climbed more than 13 percent 
among the 15 common stocks listed on the new york stock exchange 
that made new 52week highs in the week ended nov 2 nine were 
