spindler who helped launch the computermaker on a turnaround 
program will continue to report directly to john sculley apples 
chairman chief executive officer and former president spindler 
also was nominated to apples board of directors 
these actions represent strong votes of confidence in michael 
spindler and ringing endorsements of the excellent job he has done 
at apple since becoming chief operating officer in february 1990 
sculley said 
spindlers new title and sculleys relinquishing of it are 
merely formalities said apple spokeswoman barbara krause 
it really is just a title change at many fortune 100 
companies the coo is also president because it signifies 
leadership of the operational units of the company she said 
apple after several years of fast growth recently suffered a 
sales slowdown and its share of the desktop computer market fell 
critics blamed the problem on the high prices apple charged for its 
macintosh line 1799 to 11000 as clones of international 
business machines corp personal computers dominated the low end of 
the market 
but apple has overhauled its strategy hoping to trade high 
profit margins for increased sales it introduced lowcost 
macintoshes last month that start at just under 1000 
spindler who successfully headed apples european operations 
was made chief operating officer in a toplevel reorganization he 
took over sales marketing manufacturing and corporate 
communications while sculley focuses on research and development 
